 3/3/18 Flixecourt Left Amien at 11.15 get a seat in the Paris-Calai express as far as Longpr . On detrain fell in with some other Colonel most of British regiment and took a bus for the 4th Armi School at Flixecourt . A Tommi guid us to billet ? mine is rather bare but Madam seem a cheeri soul and own two daughter one a Mademoisell and the other age 7. Walk back to the H.Q . Mess and found our way into a rather palati place where they have a jolli good mess . The Chateau is a new one with wall carv and wood panel and in the Mess they have W.A.A.Cs for waitress . The Command is a full Colonel of the A Sutherland
